Name: Genius! NAZI-GIRL GoePPels-Chan ep1
About the game: This is a slightly different history to the world we know. An anti-war visual novel parody set in 1930s Germany where you play Goeppels-chan, the Minister of Propaganda, and have to keep the Fuhrer happy. The game has several routes - see if you can find the good ending. Direction/Writing Nao Minda Illustration Kiichi Voice actors Geli Goeppels/Gumi Kinoshita
